<template >

<Navbar v-if="!showNavbar" />
  


<router-view></router-view>
</template>
<script>

import Navbar from './components/Navbar.vue';



export default{
    components: {
        
        Navbar,
        
        
    },
    data(){
        return{
            showNavbar:false,
        }
    },
    created(){
        this.emitter.on('showNavbar', (evt) => {
        this.showNavbar = evt.showNavbar;
    })

    }

}
    
    
</script>
